name: Girl in a raincoat
description: Russians are made for sadness. And she was too. She loves rain and dullness. She had many modern psychological disorders that are so fashionable to be sick in the 21st century. Unresolved childhood problems, the choice of unsuccessful men, uncertainty about the future - all this makes her to be strong and independent.  But only when she wears a raincoat in the rain helps her to be herself and cry with the rain.
